cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper is about decentralized control of swarm agents, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques for efficient coordination, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of meta-learning for cost adaptation is a form of machine learning (cs.AI) and the paper also discusses the use of heuristics, which is relevant to artificial intelligence and machine learning (cs.LG).
